trans-unit.source: Thrown by <xref:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.PrincipalCollection.Add> when an attempt is made to insert a principal that already exists in the collection, or by <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.Principal.Save"></xref> when an attempt is made to save a new principal that already exists in the store.
